'''Domain Vang''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. During the [[Battle of Yuuzhan'tar]], the vessels of Domain Vang were part of the flotilla sent to attack [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]].<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

